com.socrata.model.importer

Class NonDataFileDataset

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.socrata.model.importer.DatasetInfo
      • com.socrata.model.importer.NonDataFileDataset

  • public class NonDataFileDataset
extends DatasetInfo
    Represents a non-dataset file that can be hosted by Socrata. This is normally an uploaded file. To create a NonDataFileDataset use the methods in SodaImporter.
